snippet.title: Lordz.io trailer
snippet.description: Lordz.io is the new RTS multiplayer io game ! Play online against real players. Spawn a giant army of Soldiers, Archers, Knights, Mages, Barbarians and even Dragons. Then throw yourself in the battlefield to fight against up to 20 real players worldwide. Who will become the ultimate Lordz and rank #1 on the Leaderboards?
